      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;getting-started-with-hugo&#34;&gt;Getting Started with Hugo&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo is a fast and modern static site generator written in Go. In this post, I&amp;rsquo;ll share some tips for getting started.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;why-hugo&#34;&gt;Why Hugo?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fast&lt;/strong&gt;: Hugo builds sites incredibly quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible&lt;/strong&gt;: Works with various content formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple&lt;/strong&gt;: Easy to set up and deploy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;basic-commands&#34;&gt;Basic Commands&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are some essential Hugo commands:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Create a new site&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo new site mysite
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Create a new post&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo new posts/my-post.md
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Start development server&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo server
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Build for production&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo --minify
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s it for now! More posts coming soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
